# .clang-format
---
Language:        Cpp
BasedOnStyle:    LLVM
IndentWidth:     2
TabWidth:        2
UseTab:          Never
ColumnLimit:     100

# Pointer/reference binding style (Left keeps `int* p` vs `int *p`)
PointerAlignment: Left

# Keep short functions in one line when possible
AllowShortFunctionsOnASingleLine: All

# Control how constructor initializer lists are formatted
ConstructorInitializerAllOnOneLineOrOnePerLine: true

# Don't reflow block comments aggressively
ReflowComments: false

# Keep includes ordering as-is (avoid aggressive reordering)
IncludeBlocks: Preserve

# A few spacing rules that fit embedded code readability
SpaceBeforeParens: ControlStatements
SpacesBeforeTrailingComments: 1
...
